      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches or dents, and the interior remains in pristine, original condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a complete service history and very low mileage. A buyer can expect a vehicle that requires zero investment and offers the highest level of reliability and aesthetic appeal.",
