    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe the condition of this beauty. It\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s in pristine, tip-top shape, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you're gonna love it!",
