    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new, you\u2019ve found it! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014it\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition, inside and out. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh-car feel. Honestly, it\u2019s a total gem and I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to love it just as much as I have. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
