      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This specimen exhibits an impeccable power-to-weight ratio and an 8,400 RPM redline that remains visceral and precise. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission delivers lightning-fast gear synchronization, while the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) provides adjustable damping rates for superior lateral acceleration and chassis composure. Maintenance is current with documented rod bearing prophylaxis and throttle actuator service. The factory-correct finish is flawless, and the subframe remains in factory-spec condition. A turn-key masterpiece for the serious collector demanding mechanical perfection and peak atmospheric performance.",
